y the first node.\\n- No-match output: write nothing to stdout/stderr.\\n\\n## Errors\\n\\n- Invalid XPath: stderr message, exit code `1`; message should reference `xpath`.\\n- Malformed/empty XML input: stderr message, exit code `1`; message should reference `xml`/`parse`.'\"]", "timestamp": "2026-06-04 03:38:14", "level": "verbose", "process_id": 3914271, "thread_name": "MainThread"}
